snippet.title: NRL - National Rugby League
snippet.description:
The Official YouTube Channel of the National Rugby League.  

Every week will feature exclusive interviews, highlights, and the greatest moments that the NRL has ever produced!

Subscribe and hit that notification bell to know when new videos are available here.

Follow us on social @nrl and visit NRL.com for all the latest news and updates!
